<div data-controller="appear">
  <h1 class="type-serif-heading text-center animate-fade-in-up" style="font-size: var(--text-3xl); margin-bottom: var(--space-4);">FAQ</h1>
  <p class="text-center animate-fade-in-up delay-1" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); margin-bottom: var(--space-12);">Frequently Asked Questions</p>

  <div class="space-y-6">
    <div class="card appear">
      <h2 class="card-title">When is the RSVP deadline?</h2>
      <div class="card-body">Please RSVP by the date indicated on your invitation so we can finalise headcounts, transport requirements and logistics ahead of the celebrations.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="card appear appear-delay-1">
      <h2 class="card-title">Will transfers be arranged on the wedding day?</h2>
      <div class="card-body">Yes. A dedicated transfer service will operate from select pick-up points to the ceremony at Château de Flapjack. Following the aperitif, transfers will take guests to the dinner and evening celebration, with return shuttles provided to designated drop-off points at the conclusion of the night. Please indicate in your RSVP if you wish to use this service.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="card appear">
      <h2 class="card-title">Are children invited?</h2>
      <div class="card-body">Yes - children are warmly welcomed. A professional nanny service will be arranged for families who would like support on the day. We kindly recommend that children depart after the conclusion of dinner, so parents can enjoy the remainder of the evening comfortably.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="card appear">
      <h2 class="card-title">What are the travel requirements?</h2>
      <div class="card-body">Please ensure your travel documents are valid and up to date. Check any visa requirements well in advance of your travel dates.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="card appear">
      <h2 class="card-title">What is the nearest airport, and how far is it from the venue?</h2>
      <div class="card-body">See the <%= link_to "Travel", travel_path %> page for details on nearby airports and transportation options. A rental car or pre-arranged transfer is recommended.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="card appear">
      <h2 class="card-title">What will the weather be like?</h2>
      <div class="card-body">September weather is typically warm and pleasant. A light layer is recommended for the evening.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="card appear">
      <h2 class="card-title">What if I have dietary restrictions or allergies?</h2>
      <div class="card-body">Please let us know when submitting your RSVP. We will be liaising closely with the catering teams to ensure all dietary requirements are accommodated wherever possible.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="card appear">
      <h2 class="card-title">What should I wear?</h2>
      <div class="card-body">See our <%= link_to "Attire", attire_path %> page for detailed guidance on the dress code.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="card appear">
      <h2 class="card-title">Can I bring a plus one?</h2>
      <div class="card-body">We have carefully considered our guest list. Your invitation will indicate if you have been allocated a plus one.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="card appear">
      <h2 class="card-title">Did you vibe code this website?</h2>
      <div class="card-body">
        <p>Yes! This site was built almost entirely with <a href="https://claude.ai/code" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color: var(--color-accent);">Claude Code</a>. It's a Ruby on Rails app, fully database-driven with an admin panel for managing invitations and RSVPs. It's open source — check it out on <a href="https://github.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color: var(--color-accent);">GitHub</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Gifts / Wishing Well -->
    <div class="card appear" style="background: var(--color-bg-tertiary);">
      <h2 class="card-title">What about gifts?</h2>
      <div class="card-body">
        <p>Your presence at our wedding is the greatest gift we could ask for.</p>
        <p style="margin-top: var(--space-4);">In lieu of gifts, a charitable contribution in support of a cause close to our hearts would be warmly appreciated. Details to follow.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
